xxl.core.spatial.spatialBPlusTree

Class ZBPlusTreeIndexFactrory

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.spatial.spatialBPlusTree.ZBPlusTreeIndexFactrory

  • public class ZBPlusTreeIndexFactrory
extends Object
    provides methods for creating and initializing Z-Curve Spatial Index based on B+Tree, Keys are long values. The double values of rectangles or points should be mapped to integer values.
